    {
      "instruction": "<p>Deseed your <strong>pepper[s] </strong>(scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thin strips</p><p>Crumble your<strong> chestnut mushrooms </strong>roughly</p><p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s] </strong>finely</p>",
