    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the egg is cooking, add the<strong> cooked rice </strong>to the pan with your <strong>soy sauce </strong>and give everything a good mix up until fully combined – this is your <strong>Thai-style sausage fried rice</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
