    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> Thai-style fried rice </strong>in a bowl topped with the<strong> fried egg</strong></p><p>Drizzle over your <strong>sriracha </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and top with the<strong> sliced spring onion</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
